<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 04:10:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“一旦我离开以色列国防军，我就感到自己微不足道。一周后我被征召去执行预备役任务”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-07/ty-article/.highlight/once-i-left-the-idf-i-felt-insignificant-a-week-later-i-was-called-up-for-reserve-duty/0000018f-f0af-dbca-a99f-fbff27ee0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：两个朋友正在规划他们的退伍生活，一位音乐家和舞蹈家解释了为什么跟随比领导更有意义</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-07/ty-article/.highlight/once-i-left-the-idf-i-felt-insignificant-a-week-later-i-was-called-up-for-reserve-duty/0000018f-f0af-dbca-a99f-fbff27ee0000</guid></item><item><title>全球对以色列的经济抵制获得关注，但政府没有答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-global-economic-boycott-of-israel-gains-traction-but-the-government-has-no-answers/0000018f-efc2-df2e-a5df-eff711a20000</link><description>世界正在对以色列在加沙战争中的行为失去耐心并采取措施——限制出口、取消专业会议、放弃计划中的商业交易等等。当地消费者将遭受损失</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-global-economic-boycott-of-israel-gains-traction-but-the-government-has-no-answers/0000018f-efc2-df2e-a5df-eff711a20000</guid></item><item><title>国际合法性的减弱、疲惫不堪的军队和黎巴嫩战争将把以色列推向边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/waning-intl-legitimacy-an-exhausted-army-and-war-in-lebanon-will-push-israel-to-the-edge/0000018f-ef1b-d3f3-a7ff-ff3b7db00000</link><description>与真主党的战争将是以色列后方的重大挑战：北部和中部的城市将面临前所未有的规模和火力威胁。 在加沙，哈马斯和以色列国防军之间的版本之战仍在继续，而且缺乏明确的目标正在影响疲惫的士兵 ■ 对于悲惨的以色列国防军首领赫茨尔·哈勒维来说，时间已经不多了</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/waning-intl-legitimacy-an-exhausted-army-and-war-in-lebanon-will-push-israel-to-the-edge/0000018f-ef1b-d3f3-a7ff-ff3b7db00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡使用并虐待了甘茨和艾森科特 - 但当他们离开后，他会想念他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-used-and-abused-gantz-and-eisenkot-but-hell-miss-them-when-theyre-gone/0000018f-ef1d-dff6-a9df-ef9f9adb0000</link><description>如果民族团结党兑现其巩固内塔尼亚胡联盟的威胁，他将失去保护他免受更大国际批评的防弹衣。 ■ 当总理在美国国会发表讲话时，他将重复他在 2015 年所进行的赌博 — — 并且希望有不同的结果</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-used-and-abused-gantz-and-eisenkot-but-hell-miss-them-when-theyre-gone/0000018f-ef1d-dff6-a9df-ef9f9adb0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：以色列正在倾听美国对拉法的担忧；内塔尼亚胡将于 7 月 24 日向国会发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-live/biden-israel-listened-to-u-s-concerns-on-rafah-netanyahu-to-address-congress-on-july-24/0000018f-f079-de64-a98f-f2fff0700000</link><description>以色列国防军称，突破加沙缓冲区的恐怖分子从以色列边境附近的隧道中出现 ■ 以色列国防军宣布一名在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵死亡 ■ 加沙官员称，以色列对努塞拉特学校的袭击造成 40 人死亡 ■ 巴勒斯坦权力机构因财务状况而支付一半员工工资 ■以色列国防军宣布在黎巴嫩边境附近的无人机袭击中受伤士兵死亡 ■ 三名恐怖分子在试图从加沙南部进入以色列时丧生</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 02:24:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-live/biden-israel-listened-to-u-s-concerns-on-rafah-netanyahu-to-address-congress-on-july-24/0000018f-f079-de64-a98f-f2fff0700000</guid></item><item><title>对于越来越多的以色列青少年来说，英语是逃离当地现实的一个出口</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blame-tiktok-and-youtube-why-more-and-more-israeli-teens-speak-english-among-themselves/0000018f-ef47-dff6-a9df-efd7c1c60000</link><description>他们花几个小时在 YouTube 和 TikTok 上观看美国内容，沉浸在书籍、游戏和与世界各地的人聊天的世界中，并且更喜欢与当地朋友说英语。这些以色列青少年正在逐渐摆脱希伯来语</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 22:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blame-tiktok-and-youtube-why-more-and-more-israeli-teens-speak-english-among-themselves/0000018f-ef47-dff6-a9df-efd7c1c60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将于 7 月 24 日向美国国会发表讲话，比原定日期晚六周</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/report-netanyahu-to-address-u-s-congress-on-july-24-six-weeks-after-intended-date/0000018f-ef9b-d3f3-a7ff-ffbbf3090000</link><description>尚不清楚美国总统乔·拜登是否会在城里，这可能会在两位领导人之间引发高度政治化的摊牌</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 22:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/report-netanyahu-to-address-u-s-congress-on-july-24-six-weeks-after-intended-date/0000018f-ef9b-d3f3-a7ff-ffbbf3090000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方悄悄放弃了执行圣殿山现状，尽管内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-quietly-gave-up-on-enforcing-the-temple-mount-status-quo-despite-netanyahu/0000018f-eef9-d3f3-a7ff-fef9bf9b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡很快澄清，尽管本格维尔发表了声明，但对犹太人祈祷的禁令仍然有效。但是，执行规则完全是警察的责任，他们往往对祈祷视而不见——尤其是在本-格维尔的影响下</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 20:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-quietly-gave-up-on-enforcing-the-temple-mount-status-quo-despite-netanyahu/0000018f-eef9-d3f3-a7ff-fef9bf9b0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党视频声称袭击了以色列北部的铁穹电池</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-video-claims-to-strike-iron-dome-battery-in-northern-israel/0000018f-ee34-d660-af9f-efbebca90000</link><description>如果视频属实，这将是此类防空系统据称遭到袭击的第一个有记录的实例。该发射器距离边境不到四公里，位于真主党导弹、无人机和火箭的射程深处</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 19:15:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-video-claims-to-strike-iron-dome-battery-in-northern-israel/0000018f-ee34-d660-af9f-efbebca90000</guid></item><item><title>被抛弃者与获救者：以色列男女人质会面临不同的命运吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-06/ty-article/.highlight/the-discarded-and-the-saved-will-israeli-men-and-women-hostages-face-different-fates/0000018f-ee6b-d3f3-a7ff-fe7bc2730000</link><description>在乔·拜登总统提出的停火计划第一阶段和第二阶段之间是否会恢复加沙战争的问题是主要也是最困难的障碍。如果以色列接受协议，但随后又重新开战，会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 19:11:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-06/ty-article/.highlight/the-discarded-and-the-saved-will-israeli-men-and-women-hostages-face-different-fates/0000018f-ee6b-d3f3-a7ff-fe7bc2730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方拘留在耶路撒冷国旗游行期间遭到犹太青年袭击的巴勒斯坦摄影师</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/police-detain-palestinian-photographer-who-was-attacked-by-jewish-youths-at-jlem-march/0000018f-eec9-de64-a98f-eeffbd320000</link><description>赛义夫·夸斯米 (Saif Kwasmi) 在大约 10 名犹太男孩袭击后头部受轻伤。他继续工作，后来被警方拘留，在一名知名右翼活动人士联系他们并声称夸斯米是哈马斯特工后，他的设备被没收。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 19:10:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/police-detain-palestinian-photographer-who-was-attacked-by-jewish-youths-at-jlem-march/0000018f-eec9-de64-a98f-eeffbd320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在六日战争中的神话般的胜利如何成为犹太极右翼的仇恨盛宴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/how-israels-mythic-victory-in-the-six-day-war-became-a-jewish-far-right-hate-fest/0000018f-ee29-dff6-a9df-efbbafb80000</link><description>周三，右翼以色列人庆祝六日战争中耶路撒冷的统一，以表达反阿拉伯仇恨。其丑陋的神话可能会让更多的以色列人看到军事力量的影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/how-israels-mythic-victory-in-the-six-day-war-became-a-jewish-far-right-hate-fest/0000018f-ee29-dff6-a9df-efbbafb80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列抗议者接到警方电话，要求他在骄傲集会游行中排除政治因素</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-gets-police-call-telling-him-to-bar-politics-from-march-to-pride-rally/0000018f-ee6a-d5c6-a1cf-fe7e64a30000</link><description>一名警官告诉“粉红阵线”联合创始人亚尼夫·西格尔，要确保该组织参加集会而不是通常的骄傲游行的游行中不会有“政治因素”</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protester-gets-police-call-telling-him-to-bar-politics-from-march-to-pride-rally/0000018f-ee6a-d5c6-a1cf-fe7e64a30000</guid></item><item><title>解释：“沙希德”或“烈士”对巴勒斯坦人和以色列人意味着什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/explained-what-shahid-or-martyr-means-for-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018f-e351-d1da-adaf-f7df71ae0000</link><description>自 20 世纪 90 年代巴勒斯坦自杀式爆炸事件以来，对于以色列境内讲希伯来语的人来说，“沙希德”一词一直是“恐怖分子”的代名词。现在这个词从半岛电视台到美国校园都在使用，Facebook 上禁止使用该词，并被以色列执法部门视为煽动行为，那么“烈士”对于以色列、加沙和约旦河西岸讲阿拉伯语的人来说到底意味着什么？</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:11:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/explained-what-shahid-or-martyr-means-for-palestinians-and-israelis/0000018f-e351-d1da-adaf-f7df71ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 244 天：以色列将建立伤员离开加沙系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-244-israel-to-set-up-system-for-wounded-people-to-leave-gaza/0000018f-ee78-d660-af9f-effe42820000</link><description>以色列北部指挥部负责人表示，以色列国防军已完成对真主党袭击的准备工作。 ■ 美国和其他 16 个国家呼吁以色列、哈马斯“做出一切必要的最终妥协”，以确保停战。进出加沙的病人 ■ 西班牙将加入南非国际法院的案件，指控以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝 ■ 战争进入 244 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 16:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-244-israel-to-set-up-system-for-wounded-people-to-leave-gaza/0000018f-ee78-d660-af9f-effe42820000</guid></item><item><title>认识自 1976 年以来首位代表以色列参加奥运会的阿拉伯裔以色列运动员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/meet-the-first-palestinian-athlete-to-represent-israel-at-the-olympics-since-1976/0000018f-edb5-d36e-abcf-fdf5c3d90000</link><description>即将前往巴黎的以色列游泳运动员亚当·马拉纳 (Adam Mara&amp;#39;ana) 表示：“我自己都感到惊讶，也很高兴”</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:59:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/meet-the-first-palestinian-athlete-to-represent-israel-at-the-olympics-since-1976/0000018f-edb5-d36e-abcf-fdf5c3d90000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫的骄傲活动展示了一个因战争而发生巨大变化的酷儿社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/tel-avivs-pride-events-present-a-queer-community-dramatically-changed-by-war/0000018f-edd0-d75d-a18f-efd224fe0000</link><description>同样在本周，Artport 艺术中心的年度艺术书展回归； 10 月 7 日，英雄诺姆·蒂邦 (Noam Tibon) 将成为 Fauda 创作者制作的电影的主题；死于加沙的人质查姆·佩里 (Chaim Peri) 创作的儿童读物现已出版</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:46:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/tel-avivs-pride-events-present-a-queer-community-dramatically-changed-by-war/0000018f-edd0-d75d-a18f-efd224fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列主要抗议团体针对右翼诽谤提起诽谤诉讼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/leading-israeli-protest-group-files-defamation-suits-against-right-wing-slander/0000018f-ed82-d36e-abcf-fdc6e8f60000</link><description>自哈马斯 10 月 7 日发动袭击以来的几个月里，极右翼专家经常指责以色列军队预备役组织“武装兄弟姐妹”，声称他们在反对总理内塔尼亚胡司法改革的抗议活动中呼吁拒绝服兵役，这激励了哈马斯打击以色列</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:12:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/leading-israeli-protest-group-files-defamation-suits-against-right-wing-slander/0000018f-ed82-d36e-abcf-fdc6e8f60000</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 令以色列担忧。与此同时，22 名部长迷上了这款应用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-worried-about-tiktok-meanwhile-22-of-its-ministers-are-hooked-on-the-app/0000018f-ed72-d9ce-a5cf-ffffd4610000</link><description>“TikTok 对国家安全构成战略威胁”：以色列议会的一次讨论暴露了以色列政府未能解决日益严重的操纵社交平台的问题，该平台被 380 万以色列人使用，其中包括国家安全部长</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 13:42:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-worried-about-tiktok-meanwhile-22-of-its-ministers-are-hooked-on-the-app/0000018f-ed72-d9ce-a5cf-ffffd4610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙近东救济工程处学校的袭击造成数十人死亡；以色列国防军：哈马斯利用建筑物作为基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/dozens-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-unrwa-school-in-gaza-idf-hamas-used-building-as-base/0000018f-ed20-dba5-afdf-ffb2a6480000</link><description>虽然以色列军方表示，近东救济工程处在努塞拉特的学校关押着参加 10 月 7 日的哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战恐怖分子精英，但哈马斯表示，该学校关押着流离失所的加沙人，并不是军事大院。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 11:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-06/ty-article/.premium/dozens-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-unrwa-school-in-gaza-idf-hamas-used-building-as-base/0000018f-ed20-dba5-afdf-ffb2a6480000</guid></item></channel></rss>